    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 11280: VminSearch: updating SetLimitingPatterns logic to correctly updating _lp for failing targets'
'Merged PR 11279: Cherry picking VminTC changes'
'Merged PR 11100: [VminTC] StoreSearchResults not support monolithic mode'
'Merged PR 10923: VminTC: new vmin_update_on_pass FeatureSwitch for RecoveryPort serial testing'
'Merged PR 10910: Merged PR 10832: VminTC - enable store result to shared storage'
'Merged PR 10911: Merged PR 10883: VminTC: adjust plist mode during verify using top layer content'
'Merged PR 10878: fix VminTc amble fails issue'</releaseNotes>
